name: Maintenance Item
query:
SELECT
	ms.customer as "Customer:Link/Customer:120",	
	ms.item_code as "Item Code:Link/Item:100",
	ms.barcode as "Barcode::100",
	ms.brand as "Brand::100",
	ms.model as "Model::100",
	ms.imei as "IMEI::100",

    	ms.creation as "Added Date:Datetime:120"
FROM
	`tabMaintenance Item` ms 
ORDER BY
	ms.item_code asc
